# TechNova — PWA + TWA + Play Store Implementation Plan

---

## YOUR ONLY JOB IS TO PRODUCE A PLAN

Do not install anything. Do not write any code. Do not modify any file.
Read the entire codebase, assess what exists, and produce one detailed plan document.
Nothing gets built until I approve the plan.

---

## PLATFORM COVERAGE THIS PLAN TARGETS

```
PWA (foundation — works on all platforms)
 ├── Android  → TWA → Google Play Store
 ├── iOS      → PWA install via Safari (Add to Home Screen)
 └── Desktop  → PWA install via Chrome / Edge
```

TWA (Trusted Web Activity) is Android-only. It wraps the PWA and submits it to Play Store as a real Android app. iOS App Store requires a different approach (Capacitor) and is NOT in scope for this plan.

